snippet.title: RS Analyst
snippet.description:
I'm a Reverse Speech Analyst.  On this channel I analyze the speech reversals of famous people, people in the news, historical figures, and criminals and interpret what the unconscious mind expresses through these reversals.  

The unconscious mind has no talent for deception.  It presents only truth, which is often interesting, sometimes shocking, and always amazing.
